questions.quote: But you know as soon as she gets in the apartment she's going right for that machine.
Are you kidding? I could spot that bird's nest two blocks away.
Well, I'm no genius but, according to my calculations he should be here in a few seconds.
No, no. It was an accident. It really wasn't my fault. It was Jerry.
What? Yeah.. you're right!.. All I have to do is call him up, and sit with him, and show him that it doesn't bother me. You know, laugh it off.. or jam a fork into his forehead.
Absolutely not. I mean, what are you thinking about, JERRY:? Marriage? Family?
Absolutely, you just call my secretary, she'll arrange everything.
Like in the middle of our fight last night he did this thing that he always does where he asks questions to himself, aloud. And then answers them.
Hi. You know, Kramer gave me the armoire and it is so beautiful. I'm mean, I just can't tell you how much I appreciate it.
Thank you, thank you,  Hey, Jerry, did ya see me up there? I was killing, Jerry. Killing. I killed.
